{"tid":1454622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有大本營才有升級]流水抗爭已經到左樽頸，我地要佔領機場！","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:26:56.000Z","uid":30688,"like":24,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f02cc2c53b79b6d7af749cf1609f4aa7b4f14bd8","tid":1454622,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"大家係屌我叫人重現2014佔領前，麻煩請先睇埋以下意見(第一個post講得唔清楚，重開再推)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 流水抗爭已經到左樽頸</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家有冇發現點解我地次次比人衝散？我地be water左咁耐，已經接近比人破解晒。<br />\n<br />\n成也流水敗也流水，我地如果要頂得住，唔比人拉，就要考慮其他戰術。如果次次比人衝散拉十幾個，點解唔諗過另一個方案升級？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 機場係最安全既地方</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講黑警係機場唔敢動用任何武力，但事實係黑警係機場動武，佢既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">代價一定會比起係出面任何地方都大</span></strong>。堅守離境大堂，迫使警方一係就黎清場(夠膽就黎放tear gas/開槍！)，一係就回應五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n機場有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">足夠既物資supply</span></strong>又有冷氣，除非黑警夠膽cut off 成條機場交通鏈(變相癱瘓機場)，否則大家唔使擔心物資。<br />\n<br />\n政府除左親自黎談判/ 答應要求，無野可以迫到示威者走！機場離境大堂係成場運動唯一要守既位！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 有大本營才有升級</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考烏克蘭Winter on Fire 紀錄片，點解人地果度可以守得住，裝甲車衝埋黎都攻唔入？就係因為人地有大本營。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有大本營先長期聚到人。先可以係入面大量升級武力</span></strong>，魔法師先可以做野。<br />\n<br />\n至於機場佔領係送頭定係升級，視乎有冇勇武幫手堅守機場佔領區。可以預計既係政府唔會係短期內有所回應，所以大家要有長期甚至無限期佔領既準備！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">講多次，行動正式升級，機場離境大堂要成為抗爭者大本營！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c14a93680f6c635c89c8c1438e6ffe682e9b0ea0","tid":1454622,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:00:02.000Z","msg":"推上熱門!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2e63182ec215ae1b7dc9d38e0ba542a9e39555","tid":1454622,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"推上熱門!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7fe240a4a630c1c3cb2c5e7ce5cfb197f21542","tid":1454622,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116e76a10de244ad256769fffcb13a523ea70504","tid":1454622,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f967512da7c16604068f6b7c885509dd07e67320","tid":1454622,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"有決心就有得玩，無決心就係笑話"},{"pid":"10a872c88abead273c1b498a6567a663aeee2db6","tid":1454622,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad2c8e85aac41479d34bd84c7e926dfbe27be272","tid":1454622,"uid":267328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"一定要屌<br />\n唔需要留守通頂，機場不安全，有遊客才安全"},{"pid":"0882d52434037a6989a383ff854d6b2ad0cb11df","tid":1454622,"uid":35005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"而家可能已經預備射Tgas<br />\n封晒航班"},{"pid":"ffc935216c5812f4e1301202a6bf9d822ba2cc4e","tid":1454622,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"唔需要嘉年華"},{"pid":"05dae50d826b8b68fd97502262dc0c79f30ce959","tid":1454622,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB